name: Vessels 182: Dutch
description: Dutch is a poker legend and a philanthropist.  After years of grinding and winning from the lowest stakes to the top, he now owns ‘The Palace’, a casino where the rich come to slum it and the craftiest of the poor try to push their way out of poverty.  Everyone is on an equal footing here and the games are always fair.  Dutch is widely loved throughout the colony for his family values and his powerful sense of justice.
